subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution.
Broadly distributed West Palaearctic species. Published record [omitted in catalogs by Chvála (
2012
) and Yang (
2007
)]: 
Romania
(Parvu 
2003
).

Remarks.
Collin (
1961
) provided a short redescription, and illustrations of the hind leg and genitalia. Chvála (
1983
) also redescribed this species and provided illustrations of the face, antenna, hind leg, and genitalia.
